1953;;Recoil;;British;;John Gilling;;Kieron Moore, Elizabeth Sellars;;crime;;https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Recoil_(1953_film);;When thieves rob and murder her jeweller father, Jean Talbot resolves to bring them to justice by posing as a criminal and infiltrating their gang. She builds up evidence against her father's murderer by pretending to be in love with him.